'''厄尔·西蒙斯'''（{{lang-en|Earl Simmons}}，{{bd|1970年|12月18日|2021年|4月9日}}），艺名'''DMX'''{{NoteTag|或译“深水炸弹DMX”<ref>{{cite web |title=深水炸彈 DMX |url=http://app2.atmovies.com.tw/star/sD07005789/ |website=開眼電影網 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413094700/http://app2.atmovies.com.tw/star/sD07005789/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}，美国殿堂级饒舌歌手、词曲作者、演员。西蒙斯1990年代进入饒舌界，1998年发行首张专辑《{{tsl|en|It's Dark and Hell Is Hot||It's Dark and Hell Is Hot}}》，销量口碑双丰收，首周销量达25.1万张<ref>{{cite web |first=Jason |last=Birchmeier |url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/its-dark-and-hell-is-hot-mw0000034200 |title=It's Dark and Hell Is Hot – DMX |publisher=AllMusic |date=1998-05-12 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204033311/https://www.allmusic.com/album/its-dark-and-hell-is-hot-mw0000034200 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.liveabout.com/greatest-rappers-of-all-time-2858004 |title=50 Greatest MCs of Our Time (1987–2007) |publisher=Dotdash |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531103359/https://www.liveabout.com/greatest-rappers-of-all-time-2858004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二张专辑《{{tsl|en|... And Then There Was X|... And Then There Was X}}》于1999年发行，收录单曲〈{{tsl|en|Party Up (Up in Here)|Party Up (Up in Here)}}〉。2003年单曲〈{{tsl|en|Where the Hood At?|Where the Hood At?}}〉和〈{{tsl|en|X Gon' Give It to Ya|X Gon' Give It to Ya}}〉也获得不俗的商业成绩。他是第一位五度空降[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]榜首的艺人<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-09|title=DMX, electrifying rapper who defined 2000s rap, dies at 50|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/dmx-dies/|first1=Justin|last1=Carissimo|first2=Zoe Christen|last2=Jones|access-date=2021-04-11|publisher=CBS News|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415054949/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/dmx-dies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，全球销量突破7400万<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-06-28|title=DMX Signs With CAA For Worldwide Representation|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8518074/dmx-signs-caa-worldwide-representation|first=Talor|last=Mims|access-date=2021-04-12|publisher=Billboard|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412163752/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8518074/dmx-signs-caa-worldwide-representation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

DMX还参演过电影《{{tsl|en|Belly (film)|黑道雙雄}}》、《[[致命罗密欧|致命罗密欧]]》、《{{tsl|en|Exit Wounds|以毒攻毒}}》、《[[致命摇篮|致命摇篮]]》和《{{tsl|en|Last Hour|执法先锋 (1991年电影)|执法先锋}}》，其中《致命罗密欧》和《致命摇篮》的主演包括[[李连杰|李连杰]]<ref>{{cite web |title=DMX |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/earl_simmons |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |access-date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116220203/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/earl_simmons |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年，他主演[[黑人娱乐电视台|黑人娱乐电视台]]电视真人秀《{{tsl|en|DMX: Soul of a Man|DMX：说唱之魂}}》<ref>{{cite news |last1=Haring |first1=Bruce |title=DMX Remembered Tonight By BET With Special Programming Block |url=https://deadline.com/2021/04/dmx-remembered-tonight-bet-special-programming-block-1234731459/ |access-date=2021-04-10 |work=Deadline |date=2021-04-09 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410190223/https://deadline.com/2021/04/dmx-remembered-tonight-bet-special-programming-block-1234731459/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2003年，个人回忆录《E.A.R.L.：DMX自传》（''E.A.R.L.: The Autobiography of DMX''）发表<ref>{{Cite journal | title=What's the Word: Top 10 Rap Books | url=https://www.xxlmag.com/whats-the-word-top-10-rap-books-excerpt-from-the-dec-jan-2012-issue/ | journal=XXL | first1=Adam | last1=Fleischer | first2=Jesse | last2=Gissen | first3=Mark | last3=Lelinwalla | first4=Jayson | last4=Rodriguez | date=2011-12-12 | access-date=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410043805/https://www.xxlmag.com/whats-the-word-top-10-rap-books-excerpt-from-the-dec-jan-2012-issue/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 早年 ==
1970年12月18日，厄尔·西蒙斯在[[纽约州|纽约州]][[弗農山_(紐約州)|弗農山]]出生（一说[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]）<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/rapper-dmx-dead/2021/04/09/89509a0e-9618-11eb-962b-78c1d8228819_story.html | title=DMX, chart-topping rapper with gruff voice and hardscrabble life, dies at 50 | first=Harrison | last=Smith | work=The Washington Post | date=2021-04-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409180344/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/rapper-dmx-dead/2021/04/09/89509a0e-9618-11eb-962b-78c1d8228819_story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，是19岁的阿妮特·西蒙斯（Arnett Simmons）和18岁的乔·贝克（Joe Barker）的儿子，有姐姐波尼塔（Bonita），妹妹莎拉（Shayla），以及两个夭折的弟弟<ref name=earl/>。父亲贝克是[[水彩画|水彩画]]艺人，经常画街头风景，拿去集市上卖；后来他搬到费城，经常不在西蒙斯身边<ref name=agony>{{Cite news | url=https://www.gq.com/story/dmx-obituary | title=DMX Turned Agony and Atomic Energy Into One of Rap’s Most Titanic Legacies | first=JEFF | last=WEISS | work=GQ | date=2021-04-10 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414192918/https://www.gq.com/story/dmx-obituary | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

西蒙斯患有支气管[[哮喘|哮喘]]，经常半夜睡觉无法呼吸而惊醒，要送到[[急诊室|急诊室]]<ref name=earl>{{Cite book |title=E.A.R.L.: The Autobiography of DMX |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2nUFO9VOaOcC |first1=Earl |last1=Simmons |year=2003 |publisher=HarperCollins |page=7 |first2=Smokey D. |last2=Fontaine |isbn=978-0-06-093403-3 |access-date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413173234/https://books.google.com/books?id=2nUFO9VOaOcC |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=agony/>。家人信奉[[耶和华见证人|耶和华见证人]]，直至有一次他过马路的时候被车撞到。那次事故的一个月后，保险公司代表来到他家，希望达成和解。然而她的母亲拒绝收下1万美元的和解金，说耶和华见证人的教导他们要{{tsl|en|self-sufficient|自力更生}}，不过当时该团体的教义未禁止诉讼或收受和解赔偿金。西蒙斯后来表示，如果母亲愿意收下，甚至可以因为自己的伤势索要更多<ref name=earl/>。

西蒙斯的童年十分脱节，母亲经常毒打他，换的男朋友对他很差，牙齿被打掉，脸上出现淤青和伤痕。由于家里穷，他只能睡在地板上，夜晚蟑螂和老鼠从他身上爬过<ref name=agony/>。他5岁时，一家人搬到纽约州[[揚克斯_(紐約州)|揚克斯]]的{{tsl|en|Calcagno Homes|卡尔卡尼奥家园}}<ref>{{cite web |last1=Harris |first1=Christopher |title=City of Yonkers to honor DMX |url=https://www.revolt.tv/2021/4/10/22377095/city-of-yonkers-honor-dmx |website=Revolt |accessdate=2021-04-13 |date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412215535/https://www.revolt.tv/2021/4/10/22377095/city-of-yonkers-honor-dmx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6岁时，由于不小心擦掉母亲笔记本上的东西，他被母亲用扫帚毒打，两颗牙齿被打掉。而在学校，西蒙斯也继承了母亲的坏脾气，曾把椅子抡向老师，又用铅笔刺伤一个孩子的脸<ref name=agony/>。7岁，他被姨妈用[[伏特加|伏特加]]灌醉。同年，他在市场偷蛋糕，被抓进监狱<ref name=agony/>。有一年暑假，母亲把他锁在卧室里，只允许他去浴室<ref name=agony/>。10岁，五年级的西蒙斯被学校开除后，送到朱莉娅·戴克曼·安德鲁斯儿童之家（Julia Dyckman Andrus Children's Home）住18个月。当时母亲只是说要去参观一下，之后就帮他报了名，所以西蒙斯一直认为母亲把他骗去那里，因为几个月后，他因为在里面纵火被逮捕，差点杀了他的同伙<ref name=agony/>。

14岁，西蒙斯为了逃离母亲的虐待，开始在扬克斯街头流浪，晚上住在[[救世军|救世军]]的衣服回收箱里，和[[流浪犬|流浪犬]]作伴<ref name=agony/><ref name=earl/><ref name=song>{{Cite news | url=https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/slippin-played-court-rapper-dmx-gets-year-prison-tax-evasion-n861121 | title=DMX song played in court before rapper gets a year in prison for tax evasion | first=Elizabeth | last=Chuck | work=NBC News | date=2018-03-29 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411100717/https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/slippin-played-court-rapper-dmx-gets-year-prison-tax-evasion-n861121 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。母亲知道后，把他送到一处{{tsl|en|group home|集体住宅}}，他因此结识到同住的其他纽约州学生，共同分享[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈音乐]]的爱好。朋友看完他的表演，鼓励他在老师的指导下创作音乐。回到家，西蒙斯遇到了当地的说唱歌手雷迪·罗恩（Ready Ron），对方非常欣赏他的人声口技能力，希望当他的搭档。西蒙斯给自己取了艺名DMX，出自他在男孩们的家中用过的{{tsl|en|drum machine|鼓机}}{{tsl|en|Oberheim DMX|Oberheim DMX}}，同时也有“Dark Man X”（坏人X）的含义<ref name=earl/><ref name=song/>。

在{{tsl|en|Yonkers Middle High School|扬克斯中学}}新生那年，DMX是学校田径代表队跑得第二快的人。然而他经常翘课，学习成绩很差<ref name=agony/>，要靠偷东西过活。他第一次得手是在扬克斯{{tsl|en|snatch theft|飞车偷窃}}一个装有1000美金的钱包，他用偷来的钱给自己的狗买了{{tsl|en|dog collar|狗项圈|项圈}}和{{tsl|en|dog harness|狗背带|背带}}，还有一套[[添柏岚|添柏岚]]。到了年底，他上学只为了偷东西，每天会偷3个人，之后又改为{{tsl|en|carjacking|偷车}}<ref name=agony/>。

== 音乐生涯 ==
1984年，14岁的DMX正式入行，为雷迪·罗恩做人生打击。因为偷狗数次入狱后，他开始自己写歌词，在当地的[[休闲活动|休闲中心]]为小孩子表演；1988年再因为偷车入狱，之后大部分空闲时间是在写歌词，和{{tsl|en|K-Solo|K-Solo}}一起说唱<ref name=earl/>。

同年夏天，DMX刑满释放，开始制作和销售自己的混音带，兼为其他歌曲作曲，在街角兜售，帮助他在全纽约建立粉丝基础<ref name=earl/>。1991年，获《{{tsl|en|The Source (magazine)|The Source}}》介绍独立嘻哈歌手的专栏“独立新星”（''Unsigned Hype''）点名表扬<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.cleveland.com/entertainment/2021/04/dmxs-legacy-in-12-songs.html | title=DMX’s legacy in 12 songs | first=Troy L. | last=Smith | work=Cleveland.com | date=2021-04-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411153115/https://www.cleveland.com/entertainment/2021/04/dmxs-legacy-in-12-songs.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1992年，[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]旗下的{{tsl|en|Ruffhouse Records|拉夫豪斯唱片}}签下DMX，发行了他的首支单曲〈Born Lose〉<ref name=yahoodmx>{{Cite news | title=Rapper DMX is dead at 50, family confirms | url=https://news.yahoo.com/rapper-dmx-dead-50-family-162500096.html | last=Pendleton | first=Tonya | work=Yahoo! | date=2021-04-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411100717/https://news.yahoo.com/rapper-dmx-dead-50-family-162500096.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二支单曲〈Make a Move〉于1994年发行。他还客串[[杰斯|杰斯]]、{{tsl|en|Ja Rule|Ja Rule}}和{{tsl|en|Mic Geronimo|麦克·杰罗尼莫}}的作品，1995年在麦克·杰罗尼莫首张专辑演唱经典地下说唱曲目〈Time to Build〉。

1996年9月至1998年1月，DMX开始录制个人首张专辑。当时他客串了{{tsl|en|Mase|Mase}}的单曲〈{{tsl|en|24 Hrs. to Live|24 Hrs. to Live}}〉和〈Take What's Yours〉，{{tsl|en|D-Block (hip hop)|D-Block|The LOX}}的单曲〈{{tsl|en|Money, Power & Respect (song)|Money, Power & Respect}}〉和[[LL_Cool_J|LL Cool J]]的单曲〈{{tsl|en|4, 3, 2, 1 (LL Cool J song)|4, 3, 2, 1}}〉，在独立说唱界引起剧烈反响<ref name=allmusic>{{cite web |last=Huey |first=Steve| title=DMX Biography |url={{AllMusic |class=artist |id=p68246|pure_url=yes}}|publisher=AllMusic |date=2007-06-12}}</ref>。1998年2月，DMX发行加入大厂[[Def_Jam唱片公司|Def Jam唱片公司]]后的首支单曲〈{{tsl|en|Get at Me Dog|Get at Me Dog}}〉，获[[RIAA认证|RIAA金唱片]]认证<ref>{{Cite web |last1=Vozick-Levinson |first1=Simon |last2=Buford |first2=Jayson |last3=Hoard |first3=Christian |last4=Ihaza |first4=Jeff |last5=Leight |first5=Elias |last6=Reeves |first6=Mosi |last7=Sheffield |first7=Rob |last8=Vozick-Levinson |first8=Simon |title=DMX: 16 Essential Songs |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/dmx-best-songs-1149785/ |work=Rolling Stone |date=2021-04-09 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413134003/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/dmx-best-songs-1149785/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第一场大厂专辑《{{tsl|en|It's Dark and Hell Is Hot|It's Dark and Hell Is Hot}}》于1998年5月发行，收录单曲〈{{tsl|en|Ruff Ryders' Anthem|Ruff Ryders' Anthem}}〉。专辑在美国登上[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]，销量500多万<ref>{{Cite news |last1=Brown |first1=Preezy |title=DMX's 'It's Dark And Hell Is Hot' Tracklist, Ranked |url=https://www.vibe.com/music/music-news/dmx-its-dark-and-hell-is-hot-tracklist-ranked-587279/ |work=Vibe |date=2018-05-23 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409162401/https://www.vibe.com/music/music-news/dmx-its-dark-and-hell-is-hot-tracklist-ranked-587279/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1998年12月，DMX第二张专辑《{{tsl|en|Flesh of My Flesh, Blood of My Blood|Flesh of My Flesh, Blood of My Blood}}》发行，再登上二百强榜榜首，获多铂金认证<ref name=yahoodmx/>。1999年12月21日，第三张专辑《{{tsl|en|... And Then There Was X|... And Then There Was X}}》发行<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://genius.com/albums/Dmx/And-then-there-was-x | title=...And Then There Was X | publisher=Genius | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411153115/https://genius.com/albums/Dmx/And-then-there-was-x | dead-url=no }}</ref>，使他三进二百强榜榜首，其中热门单曲〈{{tsl|en|Party Up (Up in Here)|Party Up (Up in Here)}}〉是他在[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]榜的首支十强热单，获{{tsl|en|2001 Grammy Awards|2001年格莱美奖}}{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Rap Solo Performance|格莱美奖最佳说唱个人表演|最佳说唱个人表演}}提名<ref name=grammyawards>{{Cite web |url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/dmx/11324 |title=DMX |date=2020-11-23 |website=Grammy |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413083231/https://www.grammy.com/grammys/artists/dmx/11324 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时专辑获最佳说唱专辑提名<ref name="allmusic"/><ref name=grammyawards/>。2000年，DMX客串[[魔数41|魔数41]]〈{{tsl|en|Makes No Difference|Makes No Difference}}〉的音乐录影带<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.thebiglead.com/posts/dmx-rode-an-atv-in-sum-41-s-video-for-makes-no-difference-01f2vy1p5fah | title=DMX Rode an ATV in Sum 41's Video for 'Makes No Difference' | first=Ryan | last=Phillips | work=The Big Lead | date=2021-04-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410043805/https://www.thebiglead.com/posts/dmx-rode-an-atv-in-sum-41-s-video-for-makes-no-difference-01f2vy1p5fah | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

