== 健康问题及逝世 ==
西蒙斯14岁时在雷迪·罗恩教唆他吸食掺杂了毒品的[[大麻|大麻]]香后，便染上毒瘾，开始吸食[[霹雳可卡因|霹雳可卡因]]<ref>{{Cite AV media | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwcbG1rIp8Y | title=DMX On Getting Tricked Into Smoking Crack At 14 By His Rap Mentor | work=Uproxx | via=YouTube | access-date=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-05-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524182716/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwcbG1rIp8Y }}</ref><ref name=curse/><ref>{{cite news | url=https://pagesix.com/2020/11/09/dmx-claims-his-mentor-tricked-him-into-smoking-crack-as-a-teen/ | title=DMX claims his mentor tricked him into smoking crack as a teen | first=Tashara | last=Jones | work=Page Six | date=2020-11-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410042030/https://pagesix.com/2020/11/09/dmx-claims-his-mentor-tricked-him-into-smoking-crack-as-a-teen/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也说自己是[[躁鬱症|躁鬱症]]患者<ref name=earl/>。

