rt Following Heart Attack|work=Rolling Stone|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/dmx-hospitalized-new-york-1150828/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404020743/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/dmx-hospitalized-new-york-1150828/|archive-date=2021-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Hoell|first1=Rob|last2=Cook|first2=Lauren|last3=Pittman|first3=Ava|last4=Lepore|first4=Stephen M.|date=2021-04-03|title=DMX hospitalized after heart attack amid reports of overdose: lawyer|publisher=WPIX|url=https://pix11.com/entertainment/dmx-hospitalized-after-drug-overdose-heart-attack-reports/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404024725/https://pix11.com/entertainment/dmx-hospitalized-after-drug-overdose-heart-attack-reports/|archive-date=2021-04-04}}</ref>。当晚，西蒙斯出现[[脑缺氧|脑缺氧]]，护理人员對其施行30分钟的心肺复苏<ref>{{Cite news |last1=Shafer |first1=Ellise |last2=Aswad |first2=Jem |date=2021-04-03 |title=DMX Hospitalized After Suffering Heart Attack |work=Variety |url=https://variety.com/2021/music/news/dmx-drug-overdose-1234943647/ |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404062045/https://variety.com/2021/music/news/dmx-drug-overdose-1234943647/ |archive-date=2021-04-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Alter|first=Rebecca|date=2021-04-03|title=DMX Remains On Life Support Following Overdose|work=Vulture|url=https://www.vulture.com/2021/04/dmx-is-in-critical-care-after-suffering-an-overdose.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404001849/https://www.vulture.com/2021/04/dmx-is-in-critical-care-after-suffering-an-overdose.html|archive-date=2021-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-04-03|title=Prognosis 'Not Looking Good' after OD|work=TMZ|url=https://www.tmz.com/2021/04/03/dmx-suffers-od-overdose-hospital-grave-condition/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404055001/https://www.tmz.com/2021/04/03/dmx-suffers-od-overdose-hospital-grave-condition/|archive-date=2021-04-04}}</ref>。西蒙斯经纪人纳基亚·沃克（Nakia Walker）指他已经处于“[[植物人|植物人]]”状态，肺部及大脑功能丧失，脑部无活动<ref>{{Cite news|last=Jiménez|first=Jesus|date=2021-04-04|title=DMX on Life Support in 'Vegetative State,' Manager Says|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/04/arts/dmx-hospitalized.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404211503/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/04/arts/dmx-hospitalized.html|archive-date=2021-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Dahir|first=Ikran|date=2021-04-04|title=DMX Has Been Hospitalized And Is Unresponsive, His Former Manager Says|work=BuzzFeed News|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/ikrd/dmx-hospital-unresponsive-life-support|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405000914/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/ikrd/dmx-hospital-unresponsive-life-support|archive-date=2021-04-05}}</ref>。经纪人{{tsl|en|Steve Rifkind|史蒂夫·里夫金德}}指西蒙斯处在昏睡状态，将会接受大脑功能检查，交由家人做决定<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Burke|first1=Minyvonne|last2=Dasrath|first2=Diana|date=2021-04-07|title=DMX Remains in Coma, Will Undergo Brain Function Tests: Manager|publisher=NBC News|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/doctors-perform-brain-function-tests-rapper-dmx-remains-life-support-n1263294|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407161853/https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/doctors-perform-brain-function-tests-rapper-dmx-remains-life-support-n1263294|archive-date=2021-04-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Cramer|first=Maria|date=2021-04-07|title=DMX, in a Coma, Is Set to Undergo Brain Function Tests|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/07/arts/music/dmx-life-support.html|dead-url=no|subscription=yes|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407191633/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/0