===家庭矛盾===
DMX有9个女人有染，共育有15个孩子<ref name=curse>{{cite news | url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2021/04/05/dmxs-curse-tricked-into-smoking-crack-at-14-started-lifelong-addiction/ | title=DMX's 'curse': Tricked into smoking crack at 14… | first=Martha | last=Ross | work=Mercury News | date=2021-04-05 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410064025/https://www.mercurynews.com/2021/04/05/dmxs-curse-tricked-into-smoking-crack-at-14-started-lifelong-addiction/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1999年，他与儿时玩伴塔什拉·西蒙斯（Tashera Simmons）结婚，育有四个孩子<ref name=bbcobituary>{{cite news | url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-56647793 | title=Obituary: DMX, the record-breaking rapper with bark and bite | work=BBC News | date=2021-04-09 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413141808/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-56647793 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，两人11年的婚姻于2010年7月他第一次入狱时破裂<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.vibe.com/news/entertainment/v-exclusive-tashera-simmons-talks-living-dmx-infidelity-new-chapter-40708/ | title=V Exclusive: Tashera Simmons Talks Living With DMX, Infidelity & A New Chapter | work=Vibe | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410034233/https://www.vibe.com/news/entertainment/v-exclusive-tashera-simmons-talks-living-dmx-infidelity-new-chapter-40708/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过两人仍保持关系，但2016年塔什拉指控他欠缴每月1万美元的{{tsl|en|child support|抚养}}费<ref>{{cite news |last=Ivey |first=Justin |title=DMX Welcomes His 15th Baby Into the World |url=https://www.xxlmag.com/dmx-welcomes-baby-into-world/ |work=XXL |date=2016-08-22 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410034234/https://www.xxlmag.com/dmx-welcomes-baby-into-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在和塔什拉结婚期间，DMX又有过多段外遇，其中几个人怀有他的孩子<ref name=visitors>{{cite news | url=https://nypost.com/2021/04/06/some-of-dmxs-15-kids-among-hospital-visitors-with-dad-in-icu/ | title=Some of DMX's 15 kids among hospital visitors with dad in 'vegetative state' | first=Nadine | last=DeNinno | work=New York Post | date=2021-04-06 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410051603/https://nypost.com/2021/04/06/some-of-dmxs-15-kids-among-hospital-visitors-with-dad-in-icu/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年，情妇帕特里夏·特雷霍（Patricia Terjo）起诉DMX未缴纳100万美元的子女抚养费，但案件于2013年和解<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.tmz.com/2013/12/28/dmx-baby-mama-settlement-passport-travel-europe/ | title=Settles $1M Child Support Case With Baby Mama | work=TMZ | date=2013-12-28 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413043136/https://www.tmz.com/2013/12/28/dmx-baby-mama-settlement-passport-travel-europe/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年，DMX不承认怀有马里兰州人莫妮克·韦恩（Monique Wayne）的儿子，被对方以诽谤兼未缴纳子女抚养费为由起诉<ref name=vacates>{{cite news | url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1045300/judge-vacates-15-million-judgment-vs-dmx | title=Judge Vacates $1.5 Million Judgment Vs. DMX | work=Billboard | date=2008-05-23 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410034233/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1045300/judge-vacates-15-million-judgment-vs-dmx | dead-url=no }}</ref>。经过[[基因检测|基因检测]]，孩子父亲确为DMX。2008年1月，DMX遵照法庭命令向韦恩支付150万美元，但法官于同年5月撤销了判决<ref name=vacates/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/01/11/AR2008011103371.html |title=DMX Ordered to Pay $1.5 Million |work=The Washington Post |date=2008-01-11 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627060347/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/01/11/AR2008011103371.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/10/13/AR2006101301529_pf.html |title=DMX: Call Him TBA Instead |work=The Washington Post |date=2006-10-14 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305021405/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/10/13/AR2006101301529_pf.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.today.com/popculture/judge-vacates-1-5-m-judgment-against-dmx-1C9414455 | title=Judge vacates $1.5 M judgment against DMX | date=2008-05-22 | agency=The Associated Press | publisher=Today | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410034234/https://www.today.com/popculture/judge-vacates-1-5-m-judgment-against-dmx-1C9414455 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===经济问题===
DMX三次申请破产<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://uproxx.com/movies/dmx-bankruptcy-again/ | title=DMX Is 'Drowning In Debt' And Has Reportedly Filed For Bankruptcy | first=Delenda | last=Joseph | work=Uproxx | date=2016-12-30 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410051603/https://uproxx.com/movies/dmx-bankruptcy-again/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中一次是在2013年7月30日，理据是优先考虑抚养孩子<ref>{{cite web |last=Shafferman |first=Joel M. |title=B1 (Official Form 1) Voluntary Petition(04/13) |url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/156968070/Dmx-Petition |publisher=United States Bankruptcy Court |page=9 |date=2013-07-30 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307035632/https://www.scribd.com/doc/156968070/Dmx-Petition |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但被{{tsl|en|United States Trustee Program|美国受托人计划}}质疑，于2013年11月11日被[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]{{tsl|en|U.S. Bankruptcy Court|美国破产法庭}}驳回<ref>{{cite web | last=Palank | first=Jacqueline | title=Judge Dismisses DMX Bankruptcy | url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-BANKB-19138 | work=The Wall Street Journal | date=2013-11-11 | subscription=yes | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410051602/https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-BANKB-19138 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===与拍档不和===
1990年代，DMX结识后来的说唱歌手杰斯和Ja Rule，三人有过多次合作，还组建{{tsl|en|Murder Inc. (rap group)|谋杀公司}}组合。然而该组合因为DMX和杰斯不和而拆伙。自之后DMX在采访中贬低了Ja Rule，指他抄袭成瘾，签名也是模仿他的“潦草”风格<ref name=diss>{{Cite web|url=https://genius.com/Dmx-they-want-war-ja-rule-diss-lyrics|title=DMX – They Want War (Ja Rule Diss)|website=Genius.com|accessdate=2021-04-13|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413085006/https://genius.com/Dmx-they-want-war-ja-rule-diss-lyrics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。DMX在2002年{{tsl|en|DJ Kay Slay|DJ Kay Slay}}的混音带中发布了{{tsl|en|diss track|戏谑曲}}〈They Want War〉，但Ja Rule从未直接回应<ref name=diss/>。后来DMX有意在2005年获释后结束这场纷争，但两人到了2009年才在[[VH1|VH1]]的《{{tsl|en|Hip Hop Honors|嘻哈殿堂}}》中和解<ref>{{cite news | url=https://allhiphop.com/news/dmx-officially-ends-feud-with-ja-rule/ | title=Daily News – : DMX Officially Ends Feud With Ja Rule | first=Greg | last=Watkins | work=AllHipHop | date=2009-09-24 | dead-url=no | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110118094620/http://www.allhiphop.com/stories/news/archive/2009/09/24/21952137.aspx | archive-date=2011-01-18 | accessdate=2021-04-13 }}</ref>。

DMX同样与杰斯不和。据传两人的矛盾始于1990年代早期的一场说唱大战，导致DMX对Jay-Z的不屑一顾<ref name="MTV 2015-11-10">{{cite news |url=https://www.mtv.com/news/2424398/jay-z-irv-gotti-dmx-beef-battle/ |title=IRV GOTTI EXPLAINS WHY DMX ALWAYS HATED JAY Z |work=MTV |date=2015-11-10 |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412141914/https://www.mtv.com/news/2424398/jay-z-irv-gotti-dmx-beef-battle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Meaww 2021-04-08">{{cite news |url=https://meaww.com/dmx-past-feuds-rapper-beef-jay-z-ja-rule-murder-inc-irv-gotti |title=DMX's past feuds: How rapper's beef with Jay Z and Ja Rule shattered their dreams of Murder Inc |work=Meaww |date=2021-04-08 |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412141916/https://meaww.com/dmx-past-feuds-rapper-beef-jay-z-ja-rule-murder-inc-irv-gotti |dead-url=no }}</ref>。DMX去世前，还在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上表示希望和杰斯在《{{tsl|en|Verzuz|Verzuz}}》上再斗一场<ref name="Urban Islandz 2020-05-21">{{cite news |url=https://urbanislandz.com/2020/05/21/dmx-says-eminem-dont-want-no-smoke-insist-on-battling-jay-z/ |title=DMX Says Eminem Don’t Want No Smoke, Insist On Battling JAY-Z |work=Urban Islandz |date=2020-05-21 |accessdate=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412141914/https://urbanislandz.com/2020/05/21/dmx-says-eminem-dont-want-no-smoke-insist-on-battling-jay-z/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===屡次入狱===
DMX一生入狱30次<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.gq.com/story/dmx-the-resurrection | title=Dark Man X: The Resurrection | first=Mark Anthony | last=Green | work=GQ | date=2019-09-23 | accessdate=2021-04-13 | archive-date=2021-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414060727/https://www.gq.com/story/dmx-the-resurrection | dead-url=no }}</ref>，罪名包括抢劫、殴打、劫车、虐待动物、鲁莽驾驶、酒后驾车、无证驾驶、藏有毒品、违反缓刑规定、未支付子女抚养费、冒充联邦特勤人员及逃税。

